About Allianz

Allianz Insurance is one of the largest general insurers and part of the Allianz SE Group, the largest property and casualty insurer in the world.

Allianz SE Group employs 142,000 employees worldwide, serving 85m customers in more than 70 countries.

Allianz offers commercial insurance with a full range of products for sole traders, right up to large commercial organisations. Allianz also provides car and home insurance available through a broker network, as well as pet, musical insurance and legal protection distributed through partners.
